<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.7.3">
<l>ēynta pēḻvāy vāḷeyiṟṟōrk kōḷari yāyavuṇaṉ</l>
<l>vāynta vākam vaḷḷukirāl vakirntavam māṉatiṭa</l>
<l>mōynta māvu muṭaintakuṉṟu maṉṟiyum niṉṟaḻalāl</l>
<l>tēynta vēyu mallatillāc ciṅkavēḷ kuṉṟamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of [our] lord, who sliced with sharp claws</l>
<l rend="indent">the demon’s massive chest,</l>
<l>As a fierce lion with sword[-like] teeth and an apt cavernous mouth,</l>
<l>Is Lion-Man Mountain, where there is nothing besides bamboo</l>
<l rend="indent">ravaged constantly by fires,</l>
<l>As well as broken boulders and exhausted creatures.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
